This obtion can not be used with JBOSS version lower than EAP 6.3
 
If JBOSS DB Connection monitoring through JMX, a datasource "statistics-enabled" property is required. If this property is not set, incorrect information may be gathered. This option check if this attribute is present and it is able to gather statisics information

    $JBOSS_HOME/standalone/configuration/standalone.xml
    <datasource jndi-name="java:jboss/datasources/sample" pool-name="sample" statistics-enabled="true" ...>


** This options works only with JBOSS **

---

* Default : true
* Type: Boolean
* Restart : Required
* Supported Version : 5.0.11.4